G-Good to see you.

1205
01:47:18,239 --> 01:47:19,840
—看你。-好的。
-See you later. -All right.

1206
01:47:23,844 --> 01:47:25,146
给你，亲爱的。
There you go, love.

1207
01:47:25,179 --> 01:47:26,814
